text.section:
This section applies to all traffic citations issued under this subtitle, unless:
The person otherwise is being arrested under § 26-202(a)(1), (2), (3), or (4) of this subtitle;
The person is incapacitated or otherwise unable to comply with the provisions of this section;
The citation is being issued to an unattended vehicle in violation of § 21-1003 of this article; or
The citation is being issued to an unattended motor vehicle in violation of § 13-402 of this article.
